entries.title_d: Remain in the Endor system and deliver the intercepted transmission to a command shuttle. The Inquisition will send a shuttle out to meet you.
entries.title: Dathomir System: Dropping off the Transmission
entries.split_quest_alert: Alert! High command located a Coynite command vessel in the sector. Prepare to assault and destroy command vessel.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the arrival location and wait for the arrival of the shuttle.
entries.quest_location_d: Remain in the Dathomir system and you will receive a navigation waypoint to the arrival location of the shuttle.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the broadcast to it.
entries.hello_d: Hello, pilot. I understand you have that transmission data that everyone has been waiting to get their hands on.
entries.found_loc_d: Meet the command shuttle at this location. Dock with it once it arrives to transfer the data.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Ready to begin downloading transmission data.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: We have the transmission data safely on board. Fly safe out there pilot.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Stand by for arrival of command shuttle to transfer data.
